45:57.155 --> 46:00.204
(ALBERT) Don't be such a baby.
Be careful!

46:00.366 --> 46:02.994
- (ARMAND) I can't move any faster.
- Lean on me.

46:03.161 --> 46:04.287
I need a doctor.

46:04.787 --> 46:07.131
Don't be silly.
